{
  "stem": "19807.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that's what we did then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But life overall was just wonderful there, you know, except that-- and they were very much into defense and very much in the underground.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the minute we began, I was 14, 14 and a half already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We also-- they began to train us in weaponry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They began to train us in anything military so we would know how to defend ourselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they formed this outfit with us and the day every so often, we would go on training.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we continued after that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's when we became part of the underground after that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But overall, the time in Geva, the two years, I could say that they were the most wonderful-- two of the most wonderful years I spent in my life.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I remember till today the name of the street in [INAUDIBLE] and I would drive them in Bulgarian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when we established our own kibbutz, though, and during the Israeli War of Independence, because we were besieged in the Negev for six months and they didn't receive any letters from me, they thought I was gone.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because a lot of the Bulgarian, some that came later, immediately was conscripted into the army and they really were thrown in the-- on the road to Jerusalem and they fought there and a lot of them lost their lives there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of my friends that I lost during the war, I lost them on-- in the fight of Jerusalem, not so much in the Negev as much as I lost a lot of my friends on the road to Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wouldn't say that we were in the military.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in the paramilitary, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
